Unilever Cancels Christmas Perks for Strikers, Telegraph Says

-- B y   B e n   F a r e y
-- 
2011-12-10T13:00:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-10/unilever-cancels-christmas-perks-for-strikers-telegraph-says.html
Unilever (UNA)  has canceled Christmas
parties, bonuses and hampers for U.K. workers striking about
changes to pensions, the  Daily Telegraph  reported, citing an
unnamed company spokesman.  Editors:  To contact the reporter on this story:
